      <p>1. <strong>BROWSE</strong> <br>

Browse locations across London, or let us recommend one that's right for you</p>
    </div>
     <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
       <%= image_tag 'book.png' %>
      <p>2. <strong>BOOK</strong><br>

Book in to your preferred location. Don't pay a penny until you move your stuff in</p>
    </div>
     <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
     <%= image_tag 'store.png' %>
